sql:
SELECT device_type, SUM(conversion_value) AS total_conversion_value
FROM conversions
GROUP BY device_type;

SELECT channel_id, SUM(attribution_value) AS total_attribution_value
FROM value_attribution
GROUP BY channel_id;

SELECT channel_id, website_id, traffic_date, traffic_percentage
FROM channel_traffic
WHERE traffic_status = 'active';

external_knowledge:
To calculate the percentage of direct traffic, it is assumed that direct traffic refers to traffic where the traffic percentage is 100%, indicating no involvement of other channels;
Total attributed value is a measure used to gauge the effectiveness of marketing channels;
Channels with higher total attributed values are considered more effective.

